#install.packages('ggplot2')
library(ggplot2)

##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
##    1.00    7.00   14.00   14.53   22.00   31.00
qplot(x = dob_day, data = pf, binwidth = 1)

# ggplot
ggplot(aes(x = dob_day), data = pf) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 1)

Response: Now, you may have noticed this huge spike on January first. Theres almost 8,000 users in this bin.
